title: LF Ranked Flex party/duo partners.
body:
Looking for group of players to climb ranked with/practice for next season.
Fill any role at the moment still looking for what i enjoy the most, i can play any role well.
Season 5 peaked at Diamond finished the season in Plat 1. Didnt play ranked at all Season 6 but i played placements at the end just for the rewards got placed in Gold I.
IGN: Tyron
